headline: Bio-Techne Appoints Dr. Amy E. Herr to Board of Directors
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, Feb. 4, 2025 /PRNewswire/ -- Bio-Techne Corporation today announced the appointment of Amy E. Herr, Ph.D. to serve as an independent director on the Company's Board of Directors...
